data.description: ASSUMABLE LOAN 2.7% RATE & PRICED TO SELL! Dive into the heart of the highly sought-after Rovey Farm Estates! This gem, perfectly positioned for the ultimate convenience! Just steps away from Westgate's vibrancy, and minutes from State Farm Stadium and Mattel Theme Park, entertainment is at your fingertips. Boasting a spacious 3-car garage, this home is also adorned with a tranquil backyard rose garden, creating a serene oasis amidst the city bustle. Enjoy modern comforts with recent upgrades like a NEW air conditioning unit, NEW water softener, NEW washer/dryer, and a NEW water heater. The surround sound system, wired throughout, promises immersive entertainment experiences, while the sleek stainless steel appliances cater to culinary delights. Its thoughtful split floor plan offers both comfort and functionality, ensuring privacy and ease for its residents. Priced to sell and brimming with stunning amenities, this property is a rare find. Seize this golden opportunity to call Rovey Farm Estates your new haven.
